686
00:44:45.666 --> 00:44:50.625 line:83%
Aku minum terlalu banyak
Dan semua salahmu...

687
00:44:51.166 --> 00:44:53.958 line:83%
Betapa memikat hati
Daripada gadis lemah lembut...

688
00:44:54.041 --> 00:44:56.416 line:83%
Kau sangat muda, betul?

689
00:44:56.625 --> 00:44:58.125 line:83%
Mari minum dengan seorang perempuan tua.

690
00:44:58.208 --> 00:44:59.458 line:83%
Apa kata kami nyanyi duet?

691
00:44:59.541 --> 00:45:01.333 line:83%
Betul ke?
Jadi kau memang suka gadis muda, betul?

692
00:45:01.416 --> 00:45:04.375 line:83%
Oh, terima kasih!

693
00:45:04.666 --> 00:45:07.083 line:83%
- Miki? Ini semua salah kau.
- Oh, tak apa.

694
00:45:07.583 --> 00:45:09.916 line:83%
- Apa yang awak maksudkan, "Oh, tak apa"?
- Hei, Daijin!

695
00:45:10.000 --> 00:45:11.458 line:83%
Satu gelas lagi!

696
00:45:12.500 --> 00:45:13.500 line:83%
- Apa--!?
