703
00:45:29.583 --> 00:45:32.875 line:83%
Eh, tapi bukankah dia nampak...

704
00:45:33.083 --> 00:45:34.416 line:83%
...seperti kucing?

705
00:45:34.500 --> 00:45:35.625 line:83%
Kau rasa begitu?

706
00:45:35.916 --> 00:45:38.750 line:83%
- Aku rasa dia nampak agak beradab.
- Serius!?

707
00:45:42.375 --> 00:45:43.791 line:83%
Oh, selamat datang!

708
00:45:44.000 --> 00:45:46.875 line:83%
Maaf, tapi saya kena pergi!

709
00:45:50.375 --> 00:45:52.791 line:83%
Souta! Daijin--!

710
00:45:59.416 --> 00:46:01.666 line:83%
Hei, apa yang awak--!?

711
00:46:02.875 --> 00:46:05.875 line:83%
- Suzume. Apa khabar'?
- Apa?

712
00:46:07.916 --> 00:46:09.833 line:83%
Tengok. Di sana.

713
00:46:10.791 --> 00:46:11.958 line:83%
Cacing.

714
00:46:15.875 --> 00:46:16.875 line:83%
Daijin!

715
00:46:18.375 --> 00:46:20.125 line:83%
Suzume! Kita perlu pergi.

716
00:46:20.208 --> 00:46:21.208 line:83%
Ya!

717
00:46:26.250 --> 00:46:27.916 line:83%
Gempa bumi ke?

718
00:46:28.125 --> 00:46:29.375 line:83%
Hah? Betul ke?

719
00:46:29.458 --> 00:46:31.125 line:83%
Hei, Miki.

720
00:46:31.208 --> 00:46:32.291 line:83%
Mana Suzume?

721
00:46:33.916 --> 00:46:35.541 line:83%
Di taman hiburan!

722
00:46:38.375 --> 00:46:39.875 line:83%
NOTIS PENUTUPAN

723
00:46:39.958 --> 00:46:41.875 line:83%
TERIMA KASIH UNTUK 40 TAHUN YANG HEBAT

724
00:46:48.041 --> 00:46:49.166 line:83%
Roda Ferris!

725
00:46:49.250 --> 00:46:50.625 line:83%
Telah menjadi Pintu!

726
00:46:54.125 --> 00:46:55.375 line:83%
Souta, tengok!

727
00:46:58.916 --> 00:47:00.041 line:83%
Daijin.

728
00:47:01.083 --> 00:47:04.458 line:83%
Saya akan tangkap Daijin dan tukarkan dia
kembali menjadi Batu Kunci!

729
00:47:04.541 --> 00:47:06.875 line:83%
- Semasa saya buat ini, awak...
- Ya.

730
00:47:06.958 --> 00:47:08.791 line:83%
Tutup pintu dan kunci.

731
00:47:09.166 --> 00:47:10.333 line:83%
Saya boleh buat.

732
00:47:16.958 --> 00:47:19.041 line:83%
- Tutup pintu!
- Baik!

733
00:47:25.958 --> 00:47:26.958 line:83%
Saya boleh buat!

734
00:47:32.125 --> 00:47:34.333 line:83%
Badan saya... Saya memang boleh bergerak!

735
00:47:34.416 --> 00:47:35.708 line:83%
Saya sudah terbiasa dengan badan ini!

736
00:47:36.333 --> 00:47:37.708 line:83%
Saya tak akan gagal lagi.

737
00:47:54.875 --> 00:47:56.958 line:83%
Suzume. Awak bagus saja!

738
00:48:00.250 --> 00:48:01.250 line:83%
Daijin...!

739
00:48:05.458 --> 00:48:09.125 line:83%
Hari ini, awak akan tukarkan saya balik!

740
00:48:23.791 --> 00:48:25.000 line:83%
Tengok! Lampu menyala.

741
00:48:25.250 --> 00:48:26.416 line:83%
Kenapa?

742
00:48:26.500 --> 00:48:28.500 line:83%
Bukan ke tempat itu
sudah lama ditinggalkan?

743
00:48:30.833 --> 00:48:31.875 line:83%
Apa?

744
00:48:34.666 --> 00:48:36.083 line:83%
Oh-Oh-Oh--!

745
00:48:37.000 --> 00:48:38.000 line:83%
Tunggu!

746
00:48:41.500 --> 00:48:42.500 line:83%
Serius ke!?

747
00:49:04.041 --> 00:49:05.291 line:83%
Mak...?

748
00:49:09.375 --> 00:49:11.791 line:83%
Jadi Batu Kunci, dan tutup cacing itu!

749
00:49:12.416 --> 00:49:14.958 line:83%
Tiang Timur saja tak akan bertahan.

750
00:49:15.041 --> 00:49:16.416 line:83%
- Tak boleh...
- Kenapa!?

751
00:49:16.500 --> 00:49:18.458 line:83%
Aku amanahkan tugas ini kepada kau.

752
00:49:18.541 --> 00:49:20.166 line:83%
Apa maksudnya?

753
00:49:20.250 --> 00:49:21.541 line:83%
Kau pergi.

754
00:49:22.125 --> 00:49:24.291 line:83%
Daijin akan bermain dengan Suzume.

755
00:49:24.625 --> 00:49:26.125 line:83%
Dengan Suzume?

756
00:49:30.541 --> 00:49:31.541 line:83%
Suzume!

757
00:49:31.958 --> 00:49:33.541 line:83%
Apa yang berlaku, Suzume!?

758
00:49:34.291 --> 00:49:36.791 line:83%
Apa terjadi? Apa yang awak nampak?

759
00:49:39.333 --> 00:49:41.166 line:83%
Suzume!? Datang balik.

760
00:49:41.250 --> 00:49:42.291 line:83%
Awak tak boleh masuk!

761
00:49:43.166 --> 00:49:44.291 line:83%
Suzume!

762
00:49:53.291 --> 00:49:56.250 line:83%
