810
00:52:42.333 --> 00:52:44.125 line:83%
Ya! Dengan telur mata di atas.

811
00:52:44.208 --> 00:52:45.875 line:83%
- Dan tuna-mayo!
- Ya.

812
00:52:45.958 --> 00:52:46.958 line:83%
